</div><div id='zzq8mgmk0qlrl1cRiverRapidsGadget43' class='CRiverRapidsGadget-view-rapids CRiverRapidsGadget'> <h2>Rapid Descriptions</h2>
<div><div id='zzq8mgmk0qlrl1cMessageGadget44' class='CMessageGadget-message CMessageGadget'> <div class='message  msg_message'>
<img alt='icon of message' src='/resources/images/messages/message.gif'/> No rapids entered. If you know names, and locations of the rapids please contact and advise the StreamTeam member for this run. </div>
